    h1 Denarius Wallet
  p.lead A NodeJS/MongoDB powered Denarius Web Wallet. Send and Receive DNR from anywhere!
  hr
  .row
    .col-sm-6
      h2 Fast & Secure
      p This online wallet is powered upon NodeJS/MongoDB running in conjunction with a Denarius Full Node, allowing access to the speeds and power of the Denarius blockchain.
      p
        if user
        else
          a.btn.btn-default(href='/signup', role='button') Sign Up! »
