      h2 What is Denarius?
      p Denarius is a cryptocurrency built upon the original Bitcoin Core Satoshi Nakamoto codebase. It features a new Proof-Of-Work hashing algorithm called "Tribus" and also features Proof-Of-Stake at 6% per year.
      p
        a.btn.btn-default(href='https://github.com/carsenk/denarius', target='_blank', role='button') View Github »
